{
  "stem": "27747.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I was there at my maid's home-- I could not stay in her house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She lived across from a small little forest and more like a pasture.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's where she wanted me to be.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If I am to keep you, you have to be there during the day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At night, you'll come into the barn to sleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she would bring me food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the pasture, it was very much in the open, because she lived far away from other homes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had no reason to be afraid, to keep me even at home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because each farmer was far away from each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the latest in Poland, that the farmers bought a lot of land, owned a lot of land, and were not close to each other.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because when they were close, and their roofs were out of straw, the fires would just devastate the village.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they figured out, and they built a more substantial homes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And fires did subside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said-- their reasoning was that if she was found out to shelter Jewish girls, Jewish people, she would be killed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rumors were there for a reason, so none of the Ukrainians would shelter the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I stayed there for about two to four-- two to maybe three weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was bringing me news from the town of Hoszcza, that the action did occur, that she does not know where my mother is, and that they have finished with the action, and everyone is safe to go back.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the fall in September of '42.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I knew that that wasn't true.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when she said she can't keep me anymore, I walked to the town of Hoszcza.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
